comment:
* A {@link SearchResult} includes all the information for one result item.
 *
 * @hide

variables.name: EXTRAINFO_APP_DOMAIN_URL
variables.comment: This App developer website's domain URL, String value expected.

variables.name: EXTRAINFO_APP_ICON
variables.comment: This App icon, android.graphics.drawable.Icon expected.

variables.name: EXTRAINFO_APP_DEVELOPER_NAME
variables.comment: This App developer's name, String value expected.

variables.name: EXTRAINFO_APP_SIZE_BYTES
variables.comment: This App's pkg size in bytes, Double value expected.

variables.name: EXTRAINFO_APP_STAR_RATING
variables.comment: This App developer's name, Double value expected.

variables.name: EXTRAINFO_APP_IARC
variables.comment:
* This App's IARC rating, String value expected.
     * IARC (International Age Rating Coalition) is partnered globally with major
     * content rating organizations to provide a centralized and one-stop-shop for
     * rating content on a global scale.

variables.name: EXTRAINFO_APP_REVIEW_COUNT
variables.comment: This App's review count, Double value expected.

variables.name: EXTRAINFO_APP_CONTAINS_ADS_DISCLAIMER
variables.comment: If this App contains the Ads Disclaimer, Boolean value expected.

variables.name: EXTRAINFO_APP_CONTAINS_IAP_DISCLAIMER
variables.comment: If this App contains the IAP Disclaimer, Boolean value expected.

variables.name: EXTRAINFO_SHORT_DESCRIPTION
variables.comment: This App's short description, String value expected.

variables.name: EXTRAINFO_LONG_DESCRIPTION
variables.comment: This App's long description, String value expected.

variables.name: EXTRAINFO_SCREENSHOTS
variables.comment: This App's screenshots, {@code List<ImageLoadingBundle>} value expected.

variables.name: EXTRAINFO_APP_BADGES
variables.comment: Editor's choices for this App, {@code ArrayList<String>} value expected.

variables.name: EXTRAINFO_ACTION_BUTTON_TEXT_PREREGISTERING
variables.comment: Pre-registration game's action button text, String value expected.

variables.name: EXTRAINFO_ACTION_BUTTON_IMAGE_PREREGISTERING
variables.comment: Pre-registration game's action button image, ImageLoadingBundle value expected.

variables.name: EXTRAINFO_ACTION_APP_CARD
variables.comment: Intent for tapping the app card, PendingIntent expected.

variables.name: EXTRAINFO_ACTION_INSTALL_BUTTON
variables.comment: Intent for tapping the install button, PendingIntent expected.

variables.name: EXTRAINFO_APP_PACKAGE_NAME
variables.comment: App's package name, String value expected.

variables.name: EXTRAINFO_APP_INSTALL_COUNT
variables.comment: App's install count, double value expected.

variables.name: EXTRAINFO_WEB_URL
variables.comment: Web content's URL, String value expected.

variables.name: EXTRAINFO_WEB_ICON
variables.comment: Web content's domain icon, android.graphics.drawable.Icon expected.
